1.Install nodejs and npm running the following:    
--> sudo apt-get update
--> sudo apt-get install nodejs
--> sudo apt-get npm
2. cd bidder/ 
Install depedencies , running the following
--> npm init
--> npm install express --save
--> npm install request --save-dev
--> npm install chai
--> npm install chai-http --save-dev
--> sudo ln -s /usr/bin/nodejs /usr/bin/node
--> npm install babel-preset-env --save-dev
--> touch test/test_response_bid.js


For running tests :
mocha test/test_response_bid.js
mocha test/test_empty_response.js
